With Sandusky Lee's Clear View Series Storage Cabinet, you can view your inventory and keep an eye on expensive equipment and supplies. Each of the double doors features a durable acrylic panel that allows you to see inside without unlocking the unit. The heavy-gauge steel cabinet has four adjustable shelves for items of a variety of shapes and sizes. All shelves meet ANSI/BIFMA standards. Three-point locking handles keep vandals and thieves out when class is over. Sandusky Lee's Clear View Series Storage Cabinet comes in a great selection of powder-coat paint finishes to match the décor in your school or office. Cabinet ships fully assembled; the handle requires easy assembly. $334.95 - $569.95
